-- CBS Chief Moonves Expects Continued Increases in Local Advertising Sales
-- B y   S a r a h   R a b i l
-- 2010-12-07T21:43:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-07/cbs-chief-moonves-expects-continued-increases-in-local-advertising-sales.html
CBS Corp. Chief Executive Officer
Leslie Moonves said he expects local advertising revenue gains
in the first quarter to equal gains the company posted in the
third and fourth quarters.  Moonves spoke today at the UBS Global Media and
Communications Conference in New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah Rabil in New York at 
